<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 6:45
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='390000' id='t-390000'>So Jawbone is a project that you're familiar with,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='396000' id='t-396000'>and it has a humanistic technology.</span>
