<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='411000' id='t-411000'>But the other thing that is humanistic about Jawbone</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='413000' id='t-413000'>is that we really decided to take out all the techie stuff,</span>
