<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='439000' id='t-439000'>And this is what we're pursuing here.</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 7:37
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='442000' id='t-442000'>But how we work on Jawbone is really unique.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='446000' id='t-446000'>I want to point at something here, on the left.</span>
