<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='491000' id='t-491000'>And then, of course, design is never done.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='493000' id='t-493000'>And this is -- the other new way that is unique</span>
